	   <tr><td colspan=2>Just to clear things up, people do NOT roll on phat lewts from statue, its awarded by the guild leader for you will be in a guild or trying out for one when killing this MOB.  My guild and i did this last night, Killed vindicator first and then went to Statue.  The way to kill him is to get malo/bard debuff-tashania/RO/slow/whatever else is you can on him.  Once slowed, he is not a very hard mob, if he is duel weilding, i would suggest slowing him very FAST for he will be kicking the f*cking bejezus out of your tanks and they will go down.  These items are great off him.  He dropped the BP/cloak/reaver last night.  Very nice lewts, the BP went to a warrior and cloak went to a rogue.  This isnt an easy mob to kill but we managed to rape him on our first attempt with very few deaths.<br><br>57 wizard out<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
